<item>
            <title>[LU-5352] bad if condition in dt_index_read()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5352</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In dt_index_read() we test to if the unsigned int rdpg-&amp;gt;rp_count is &amp;lt;= 0 and a multiple of LU_PAGE_SIZE:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;        /* rp_count shouldn&apos;t be &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; and should be a multiple of the container           
         * size */
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rdpg-&amp;gt;rp_count &amp;lt;= 0 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; (rdpg-&amp;gt;rp_count &amp;amp; (LU_PAGE_SIZE - 1)) != 0)
                RETURN(-EFAULT);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &apos;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&apos; should be &apos;||&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was found using the clang analyzer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
